parameters.name: Name
parameters.description: The name of the trust store. This name must be unique per region and can't be changed after creation.

parameters.name: CaCertificatesBundleS3Bucket
parameters.description: The Amazon S3 bucket for the ca certificates bundle.

parameters.name: CaCertificatesBundleS3Key
parameters.description: The Amazon S3 path for the ca certificates bundle.

parameters.name: Tags
parameters.description: The tags to assign to the trust store. (dict) --- Information about a tag. The key of the tag. Value (string) --- The value of the tag.

nested_items.name: TrustStores
nested_items.description: Information about the trust store created.

nested_items.name: Name
nested_items.description: The name of the trust store.

nested_items.name: TrustStoreArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the trust store.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The current status of the trust store.

nested_items.name: NumberOfCaCertificates
nested_items.description: The number of ca certificates in the trust store.

nested_items.name: TotalRevokedEntries
nested_items.description: The number of revoked certificates in the trust store.
